<style>
    body {
        margin: 0 !important;
        min-height: 100vh !important;
        overflow-x: hidden !important;
        background:
            radial-gradient(circle at 12% 18%, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.22), transparent 28%),
            radial-gradient(circle at 82% 14%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.30), transparent 34%),
            linear-gradient(135deg, #020617 0%, #070b1d 45%, #020617 100%) !important;
        font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif !important;
    }

    body::before {
        content: "";
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
            linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.035) 1px, transparent 1px),
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.035) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 42px 42px;
        pointer-events: none;
        animation: gridMove 18s linear infinite;
    }

    .login-page {
        min-height: 100vh;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .login-shell {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1.25fr;
        gap: 46px;
        align-items: center;
        max-width: 1340px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 54px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .login-card,
    .login-info-card {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 34px;
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.78) !important;
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.20) !important;
        box-shadow:
            0 30px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.58),
            inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06) !important;
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }

    .login-card {
        padding: 44px;
        animation: loginFloat 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .login-info-card {
        padding: 46px;
        animation: loginFloat 7s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
    }

    .login-logo {
        width: 84px;
        height: 84px;
        border-radius: 28px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        font-size: 36px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef233c, #b91c1c);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(239, 35, 60, 0.42);
        margin-bottom: 22px;
        animation: logoPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .login-kicker {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 9px 16px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.12);
        border: 1px solid rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.32);
        color: #fecaca;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .login-card h1,
    .login-info-card h1 {
        margin: 18px 0 18px;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 68px);
        line-height: 0.96;
        font-weight: 950;
        letter-spacing: -0.06em;
        text-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    }

    .login-card p,
    .login-info-card p {
        color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.78);
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .login-discord-btn {
        margin-top: 28px;
        height: 64px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 950;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #2563eb, #06b6d4);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.38);
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, filter 0.2s ease;
    }

    .login-discord-btn:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.01);
        box-shadow: 0 26px 60px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.52);
        filter: brightness(1.08);
    }

    .login-role-grid,
    .login-feature-grid,
    .login-status-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 22px;
    }

    .login-role-card,
    .login-feature-card,
    .login-status-card {
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 18px;
        background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.48) !important;
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.14) !important;
        transition: transform 0.22s ease, border-color 0.22s ease, background 0.22s ease;
    }

    .login-role-card:hover,
    .login-feature-card:hover,
    .login-status-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.42) !important;
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.78) !important;
    }

    .login-feature-card {
        display: flex;
        gap: 14px;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .login-feature-card span {
        width: 46px;
        height: 46px;
        flex: 0 0 46px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.18);
        border: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.25);
        font-size: 22px;
    }

    .login-feature-card h3,
    .login-role-card h3,
    .login-status-card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 6px;
        color: white;
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 950;
    }

    .login-feature-card p,
    .login-role-card p,
    .login-status-card p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.45;
        color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.74);
    }

    .login-online {
        position: absolute;
        right: 46px;
        top: 42px;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        color: #86efac;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-size: 13px;
    }

    .login-online::before {
        content: "";
        width: 10px;
        height: 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #22c55e;
        box-shadow: 0 0 18px #22c55e;
    }

    @keyframes loginFloat {
        0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
        50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
    }

    @keyframes logoPulse {
        0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(239, 35, 60, 0.42); }
        50% { box-shadow: 0 26px 70px rgba(239, 35, 60, 0.62); }
    }

    @keyframes gridMove {
        from { background-position: 0 0; }
        to { background-position: 42px 42px; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1050px) {
        .login-shell {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            padding: 28px;
        }

        .login-card h1,
        .login-info-card h1 {
            font-size: 46px;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 650px) {
        .login-shell {
            padding: 16px;
        }

        .login-card,
        .login-info-card {
            padding: 26px;
            border-radius: 26px;
        }

        .login-role-grid,
        .login-feature-grid,
        .login-status-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>

<style>
body {
    background: red !important;
}
</style>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LSMD Abteilungszentrale Login</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body class="ultra-login-body">

    <div class="ultra-grid"></div>
    <div class="ultra-orb ultra-orb-red"></div>
    <div class="ultra-orb ultra-orb-blue"></div>
    <div class="ultra-orb ultra-orb-green"></div>

    <main class="ultra-login-wrapper">
        <section class="ultra-login-card">
            <div class="ultra-logo">
                <span>🚑</span>
            </div>

            <div class="ultra-access-badge">
                LSMD ACCESS SYSTEM
            </div>

            <h1>
                LSMD Abteilungs<br>
                Dashboard
            </h1>

            <p class="ultra-login-text">
                Melde dich mit Discord an und verwalte Ausbildungstermine,
                Mitglieder, Dokumente und Overwatch zentral im LSMD-System.
            </p>

            <a href="/auth/discord" class="ultra-discord-btn">
                <span>💬</span>
                Mit Discord einloggen
            </a>

            <div class="ultra-role-grid">
                <div>
                    <strong>Admin</strong>
                    <p>Voller Zugriff</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <strong>LSMD Abteilungszentrale</strong>
                    <p>Dashboard Zugriff</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p class="ultra-small-note">
                Zugriff nur mit g&uuml;ltiger Discord-Rolle.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="ultra-info-panel">
            <div class="ultra-panel-top">
                <span>LIVE SYSTEM</span>
                <strong>Online</strong>
            </div>

            <h2>Abteilungen. Verwaltung. Kontrolle.</h2>

            <p>
                Die LSMD Abteilungszentrale verbindet Discord-Login,
                Rollenpr&uuml;fung, Punkteverwaltung, Dokumente und MD-Eintr&auml;ge
                in einem modernen System.
            </p>

            <div class="ultra-feature-stack">
                <div class="ultra-feature-card">
                    <span>📅</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Abteilungen</strong>
                        <p>Fahrfreigaben und Sanit&auml;ter-Pr&uuml;fungen sauber dokumentieren.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="ultra-feature-card">
                    <span>👥</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Mitglieder & Punkte</strong>
                        <p>Wochenziel, Rang und Punkteverwaltung auf einen Blick.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="ultra-feature-card">
                    <span>📄</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Dokumente</strong>
                        <p>Leitf&auml;den, Regelwerke und Checklisten zentral abrufen.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="ultra-feature-card">
                    <span>🛡️</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Admin Tools</strong>
                        <p>Spontane-Pr&uuml;fungen Panel direkt per Discord senden.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ultra-system-row">
                <div>
                    <strong>Discord</strong>
                    <span>Verbunden</span>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <strong>MongoDB</strong>
                    <span>Online</span>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <strong>LSMD</strong>
                    <span>Bereit</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

</body>
</html>